Text: FROM BILL SWANSTROMProject White Knight Cc Message From Ingram Kay Sent Wednesday September AM To Cc Brownell Stephen Swanstrom Bill Subject FROM BILL SWANSTROMProject White Knight As a followup to my earlier email regarding Steve Brownells experience regarding municipalization strategies as a way to facilitate Enrons efforts to be the energy manager for communities I have attached a proposal pursuant to which you can potentially use taxexempt financing to restructure power contracts Let me know if you or anyone else over there are interested in talking about this further I think its an interesting idea Kay Ingram Assistant to H William Swanstrom Locke Liddell Sapp
